title: Dubai Bus on Demand
description:
Dubai Bus on Demand is quick, affordable, smart and efficient way of traveling within Dubai’s major zones and get connected with city, brought to you by the Road and Transport Authority, powered by Via and United Trans. 
 
Just download the Dubai Bus On-Demand app today, sign up, book your ride and go where & when you want within the areas. It is as easy as click, pay and go.
 
Our intelligent service allows passengers to share their journey with others on similar routes. Book a journey and our powerful algorithm matches you with a premium vehicle that will pick you up at the closest convenient spot. Dubai Bus on Demand is a new model of on-demand transport; a technology-enabled vehicle to a street near you, when and where you need.
 
How does Dubai Bus On-Demand work?
Dubai Bus On-Demand is an on-demand travel concept that takes multiple passengers heading in the same direction and books them into a shared vehicle. Using the Dubai Bus On-Demand app, input your address and we’ll match you with a vehicle going your way. We’ll pick you up on a nearby corner and drop you off within a few streets of your requested destination. Our smart algorithms provide journey times that are comparable to a taxi and much more convenient than other modes of travel.

How long will I wait?
You'll always get an accurate estimate of your pick-up ETA before booking. You can also track your minibus in real time in the app.
 
How many passengers will I share a vehicle with?
The number of passengers you will share a journey with varies based on capacity and your chosen destination. Our comfortable minibuses can easily accommodate up to 14 people.

What else do I need to know about using the service?
If you require the use of a wheelchair space, you can mark yourself in the app under your rider profile. 
 
Try this new on-demand transport app that is guaranteed to change the way that you think about travelling. We look forward to seeing you on your next journey. Just click, pay, go!
 
Love our app? Please rate us! Questions? Please contact us at help@thebusondemand.com

title: REVIERFLITZER
description:
REVIERFLITZER is the on-demand shuttle that complements public transport late in the evening and at night provided by STOAG. In the north of Oberhausen and in Neue Mitte we will bring you safely and comfortably from A to B. During your ride, you will be sharing the REVIERFLITZER with other riders traveling in a similar direction. This helps to reduce traffic congestion, save resources and improve the quality of life and climate in Oberhausen.
 
You can pay for your ride directly in the REVIERFLTZER app by credit card or PayPal. The ride price is based on the current VRR-tariff system and depends on the amount of kilometers travelled and whether or not you have a valid public transport ticket. Of course any ride delays caused by traffic or detours due to the picking up or dropping off other riders will not be reflected in the price you pay. You will be shown the final price of your trip before accepting the ride.

REVIERFLITZER will transport you safely to your destination on Mondays to Thursdays from 21:00 - 02:00, Fridays from 21:00 - 06:00, Saturdays from 21:00 - 09:00 and Sundays from 21:00 - 2:00. 
 
Download the REVIERFLITZER-app for free, register and share your ride!

How it works: 

Enter your origin and destination (either by entering the address or by moving the pin on the map) 
 
Adjust the passenger count and the available public transport tickets
 
Accept ride (you will see the final price before accepting) 
 
Be picked up from a REVIERFLITZER and transported to your destination (you can see your REVIERFLITZER and route in the app) 
 
After your ride pay by credit card or PayPal through the app.

title: Barrie TOD
description:
Barrie Transit ON Demand is here. Download the app. Book your ride. Get moving now!

Barrie Transit ON Demand is a new way to provide transit service in Barrie. This pilot project offers on demand, shared-ride transportation intended to connect people along Barrie Transit bus route #11 – from Huronia Rd. and Lockhart Rd. to Bayview Dr. and Little Ave.

Transit ON Demand is a transit service without a fixed schedule where buses only make stops upon request via a mobile app. Riders simply select a time for their ride and their start location. The app will let riders know when to expect a ride, where to wait and when they will reach their destination. Trips can be booked up to 7 days in advance with payment made in the app.

Benefits to Transit ON Demand include:

- On demand trip booking up to 7 days in advance
- Shorter pick-up windows
- Faster trips as stops only occur as requested
- More efficient service

How it works:

- Download the free “Barrie Transit ON Demand” app from your app store
- Enter your starting point and destination (these areas are highlighted in the app)
- Select the date and time you want to ride up to 7 days in advance
- Provide rider information (number of riders, adult/youth, wheelchair, etc.)
- Select your payment option: pass, ticket, transfer or pay in the app with a credit card
- The app lets you know when to expect your ride and where to wait

title: Edmonton On Demand Transit
description:
Edmonton On Demand Transit service is available 7 days a week to connect select areas of the city that don’t have a regular bus route to Edmonton’s transit network. This service is operated on behalf of the City of Edmonton by PWTransit Canada in partnership with Via Transportation.

What does on-demand mean?
It means you can get a ride when you need it. No more bus schedules and shorter wait times.

How does Edmonton On Demand Transit work?
You can book a ride on an accessible shuttle bus by using this app on a smartphone, visiting the website edmonton.ca/OnDemandTransit or calling 780-496-2400.

How do I get started?
Start by downloading the Edmonton On Demand Transit app, then create an easy account using only your name, phone number and email address. Confirm your location and input your destination to see the ride options. Then, book your ride and track it in real time. If you are calling in, provide the same information to the representative who will give you step by step instructions.  

Who is driving the buses?
Professionally-trained drivers from PWTransit will operate the On Demand Transit shuttle buses.

How long will I wait?
It depends on your trip and the time of day – but wait times will be less than 30 minutes in peak times and 60 minutes in off peak times. An accurate estimate of your wait time will be provided before you book your trip. You will be able to track the vehicle location in real-time using the Edmonton On Demand Transit app.

What else is helpful to know?
If you use a wheelchair or other mobility device, have a child stroller or need access to a built-in child safety seat, it’s important to put that in your Edmonton On Demand Transit booking or mention that to the phone representative. That way, we can ensure a spot is available for you.

Why are you offering this new service?
To provide connection to the regular Edmonton transit network from areas where flexible On Demand Transit is a better fit than big bus service.

title: GoShare: Deliver, Move, LTL
description:
GoShare is the best app for finding & booking local delivery & moving professionals on demand. GoShare is one of the largest networks of truck owners, van owners & delivery professionals in the US. Our innovative technology & crowd-sourced model has made us one of the fastest growing businesses in America.

People use GoShare for moving help & delivery services. Moving help includes a truck or van & 1 or 2 movers. Business shippers use GoShare to improve the last mile & middle mile of their supply chain with our same day delivery solutions & nationwide network of delivery pros. We support multi-stop delivery routes, hot shot deliveries & offer same day service.

The GoShare app makes it easy to get things done fast. You tell us what you’re moving, where we need to take it and when. We’ll deliver locally or long distance in a truck, van or car that fits your needs at a price that fits your budget. In just a few clicks you can easily book a delivery professional for anything from a small apartment move to a shipment of pallets. We can deliver small parcels or big & bulky items on demand.

With GoShare you’ll get the best prices, high-quality service & background checked delivery professionals that care about your satisfaction. Our thorough vetting process ensures that each delivery pro has the experience necessary to get the job done efficiently & safely.

Our delivery professionals will load, deliver & unload your cargo. You can hire one or two delivery pros with a box truck, cargo van, pickup or car depending on the size of the load & how much help you need. For moving big & bulky items we recommend that you select two delivery pros unless you are able to provide loading & unloading assistance.

The GoShare app allows you to track the status of your delivery with real-time notifications. You can communicate directly with your driver in the app. After your delivery is complete you can rate your delivery pros & pay through the app. Your ratings & feedback help us build a solid, dependable community of service providers for our valued customers.

Every project booked through GoShare is covered by our comprehensive cargo, liability & auto insurance policies. Say goodbye to long delivery windows. Set a time that works for you. Schedule a pickup 7 days a week between 5:00am-11:30pm.

Download the app to get a fair & transparent upfront price estimate. Save 50% compared to traditional providers. Our app makes it easier than ever to book, track, communicate & pay. Request a delivery professional in one minute. White glove service & assembly is available for most items.

Special equipment such as a lift gate, dolly, appliance dolly, furniture dolly, lumber rack & more can be requested in the app. Our customer service team is available 7 days a week to help you get moving & answer any questions. You can chat with our team in the app or on our website.

Ways people use GoShare:
• Moving Help
• Retail Delivery
• Donation Pickup
• Moving In or Out of a Storage Unit
• Facebook Marketplace, Craigslist or Offerup pickup & delivery
• Furniture Delivery

Ways businesses use GoShare:
• Last Mile Delivery
• Local & Long Distance Freight Shipping
• Courier Service

• 3rd Party Logistics (3PL)

Industries that use GoShare:
• Retail & Wholesale

Service not available in every city. As long as the pickup or drop off address is inside one of our coverage areas we can accept your delivery request. We are consistently adding new states & expanding our coverage area.

title: GoShare Driver: Earn Money
description:
Be your own boss, work when you want, & get paid weekly with GoShare! Earn money driving your pickup truck, cargo van, box truck, sedan or SUV in your community.

GoShare is the best app for truck, van & car owners to find local delivery & moving work on demand. GoShare is one of the largest networks of truck owners, van owners & delivery professionals in the US. Our innovative technology & crowd-sourced model has made us one of the fastest growing businesses in America.

GoShare connects independent delivery professionals with businesses & people who need help moving or delivering on demand. Turn your vehicle from a liability that is costing you money every month into an asset that is earning you money.

Trusted by more than 20,000 delivery professionals & over 100,000 customers including: Costco, HomeGoods, Tesla, Pepsi, Sherwin-Williams, CAT & Living Spaces

Earnings*:
Pickup Truck: average rates up to $70 per hour
Cargo Van: average rates up to $105 per hour
Box Truck: average rates up to $168 per hour
Courier: average rates up to $45 per hour

Plus 100% of your tips

How it works:
Sign up at https://goshare.co/trucks/drivers/apply
Watch information video
Complete background check
Pass vehicle inspection
Start earning money

GoShare pays some of the highest per hour earnings in the logistics industry. Our top delivery pros earn thousands of dollars per month. Use the app to manage your delivery & moving business. As an independent contractor there is no need to let us know when you take time off. You control when you work. GoShare does not employ delivery professionals.

GoShare handles payments & collections. You typically get paid within 3-4 business days. Enjoy access to discounts on healthcare, GM vehicles, tires, cash advances & more. Win cash & other prizes in one of our many contests.

We're great at marketing, customer service & building apps to make your business run smoothly so you can focus on what you do best, delivering to customers.

GoShare is like a load board that comes to you. Our relationships with businesses keeps a steady stream of loads coming your way. You may be notified through the app when a new load in your area is available. We provide all of the tools you need to run your delivery business including: payments, marketing, customer service, proof of delivery & more. You can focus on driving & delivering.

All delivery professionals must be at least 18 years old & own or lease a vehicle with a model year of 2001 or newer. Must also be able to lift & carry at least 50 lbs.

GoShare is not only about making money. We’re about building a community of delivery pros who want to improve their lives. See why delivery pros nationwide choose GoShare: https://youtu.be/JYzUhl9clUo

GoShare is currently available in select cities within: Arizona, California, Colorado, Connecticut, Delaware, Florida, Georgia, Illinois, Indiana, Kansas, Kentucky, Louisiana, Massachusetts, Maryland, Michigan, Minnesota, Missouri, Nevada, New Jersey, New York, North Carolina, Ohio, Oklahoma, Oregon, Pennsylvania, South Carolina, Tennessee, Texas, Utah, Virginia, Washington, Washington DC.

If GoShare is not in your area signup online & we’ll retain your info until we launch in your area. You will be notified first once GoShare becomes available. If you are looking to run your own delivery business, a side hustle, delivery or hot shot gigs GoShare may be a good fit.

title: Yoshi - Keep Moving
description:
Yoshi delivers gas, washes and oil changes directly to your car! Simply enter your location in the Yoshi app, choose your preferred weekly schedule and Yoshi will take care of the rest.

Yoshi helps you take care of your car while saving you time and money. Yoshi matches per-gallon gas prices every day with the lowest-priced Top-Tier™ gas station in your area, so you can rest assured that you are getting the best price! No more stopping for gas, no more stopping for a car wash or oil change, and no more driving across town to find reasonably priced gas.

In addition to cheaper gas prices, our customers save an average of $240, 33 hours, and 3 trees when using Yoshi over the course of a year.

$240 — We provide discounts on fuel prices and additional discounts when you add car maintenance services
33 hours — We save drivers time by bringing the gas and car maintenance to them
3 trees — With one year of Yoshi, you save the CO₂ that three trees would consume (over 150 pounds). Yoshi maintains your tire’s air pressure to ensure your car
